@ToDoList_HostAddress = http://localhost:5179

### UserController - Get user by ID
GET {{ToDoList_HostAddress}}/user/by-id/1
Accept: application/json

###

### UserController - Filter users
POST {{ToDoList_HostAddress}}/user/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "john",
  "FullName": "John Doe",
  "IsAdmin": true,
  "StateFilter": [1, 2]
}

###

### UserController - Create user
POST {{ToDoList_HostAddress}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "newuser",
  "FullName": "New User",
  "Password": "password123",
  "Status": 1,
  "IsAdmin": false
}

###

### UserController - Update user
PUT {{ToDoList_HostAddress}}/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Username": "updateduser",
  "FullName": "Updated User",
  "Password": "newpassword",
  "Status": 2,
  "IsAdmin": true
}

###

### UserController - Delete user
DELETE {{ToDoList_HostAddress}}/user/1

###

